# ✅ SAFE & CORRECT WAY (STEP-BY-STEP)

## 🔥 STEP 1: Decode current config

```bash
oc get secret dev-console-console-secret -n dev-kafka \
-o jsonpath='{.data.console-config\.yaml}' | base64 -d > console-config.yaml
```

---

## 🔥 STEP 2: Edit file

```bash
vi console-config.yaml
```

---

### ✏️ CHANGE THIS

#### ❌ OLD

```yaml
url: "https://thanos-querier-openshift-monitoring.apps.dev.sbiepay.sbi"
```

#### ✅ NEW (FINAL FIX)

```yaml
url: "http://thanos-querier.openshift-monitoring.svc:9091"
```

---

## 🔥 STEP 3: Encode back

```bash
cat console-config.yaml | base64 -w 0 > encoded.txt
```

---

## 🔥 STEP 4: Patch secret (SAFE METHOD)

```bash
oc patch secret dev-console-console-secret -n dev-kafka \
--type='json' \
-p='[{"op":"replace","path":"/data/console-config.yaml","value":"'$(cat encoded.txt)'"}]'
```

---

## 🔥 STEP 5: Restart console

```bash
oc rollout restart deployment/dev-console-console-deployment -n dev-kafka
```

